=Description=

"DeOS is a secure, private, Decentralized Operating System. With its revolutionary blockchain driven, decentralized operating system. DeOS is secure, private, free and global.

DeOS includes a native BitCoin Wallet, supported by a curated digital currency business suite, giving the currently millions unbanked of the world a free secure digital wallet they can start using today.

DeOS contains a set of cutting edge free cloud services, including a full cloud office suite. Detailed descriptions of these services are on the DeOS Apps & Services page. DeOS also automatically syncs your devices, updates your documents and backs up your important information. DeOS includes free ad-free email, and a find my device app and is available now as a free download."
(http://www.razormind.co.uk/news/2015/5/6/deos)

